        "content": "### Cost and agent-attribution boundary\n\nThe pinned agentgateway exports token histograms and cost-catalog **lookup status**, but no Prometheus currency-cost value. Its GenAI labels include provider, request/response model, and route, but no stable Fgentic agent identity. Exact currency spend and per-agent cost therefore require a versioned price catalog plus an explicit delegation-to-LLM correlation metric; this dashboard does not estimate or fabricate either value.",
